I"?<p>Python fstrings can be written as follows:<br />
f”{[variable]:[modifiers][width].[#decimals][format]}”</p>
<h3 id="modifiers">modifiers:</h3>
<p>The modifiers are:</p>
<ul>
  <li>+  =   include sign</li>
  <li>x&gt; = right align (x for padding)</li>
  <li>x&lt; = left align (x for padding)</li>
  <li>x^ = centre align (x for padding)</li>
  <li>, = format with comma</li>
</ul>

<h3 id="format">format:</h3>
<p>The format is one of:</p>
<ul>
  <li>d = integer</li>
  <li>f = float</li>
  <li>e = exponent notation</li>
  <li>% = format with percentages</li>
</ul>
:ET